@plan
title: Adopt the WTB-plan!
subtitle: Convincing the rest of the party to support the WTB-plan.
choose-if: advisor_action_timer <= 0 and wtb_adopted == 0 and wtb_support >= 3 and black_thursday_seen and (not historical_mode or ((labor_strength >= agrarian_strength) and (labor_strength >= left_strength) and (labor_strength >= reformist_strength)))
